function calculate()
                local duration_ms = duration_ms or 0.0
                local wduration = math.max(math.min(duration_ms / 1000.0, 400.0), 0.1)
                local wdud = watch_time_under_duration_probabilities_origin_orig or 0.5
                local wdsr = wdud * (wduration ^ (wdud - 0.05))
                -- print("fenghan", duration_ms, wduration, watch_time_under_duration_probabilities_origin_orig, wdud, wdsr)
                return wdsr
            end
